description:
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a highly motivated and enthusiastic individuals to work within Mental Health Unit based in Heddfan. The candidate will need to have excellent communication and interpersonal skills. The individual will need to be flexible and dynamic in their approach in delivering care to both patients and carers. The individual will work as a member of the team, working towards the provision of assessment and treatment of older persons. The post holder will need to be an effective team player and be committed to providing the highest standards of care.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We welcome Nurses from Adult, Mental Health and Learning Disabilities backgrounds. We provide a full induction programme.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;The ability to speak Welsh is desirable for this post; Welsh and / or English speakers are welcome to apply.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Closing Date : 15 November 2020&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
